===Noun===
'''gluon''' (''plural'' '''gluons''')
{{wikipedia}}
# {{particles}} A [[gauge boson]] that binds [[quark]]s together to form [[baryon]]s, [[meson]]s and other [[hadron]]s and is associated with the [[strong nuclear]] force.

